{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "pet360-fiap-2026-collection",
    "name": "Pet360 — Challenge FIAP Java Advanced 2026",
    "description": "Coleção completa para testes da API REST do Pet360 (CLYVO VET).\n\n**Como usar:**\n1. Suba a aplicação com `./gradlew bootRun`\n2. Execute a request `Auth → Login (admin)` — o token será salvo automaticamente em `{{token}}`\n3. Todas as outras requests usam Bearer Auth com esse token\n\n**Variáveis:**\n- `baseUrl` = http://localhost:8080\n- `token` = preenchido após login\n- `tutorId`, `clinicaId`, `petId`, `consultaId`, `vacinaId`, `medicamentoId`, `agendamentoId`, `alertaId` = capturados automaticamente após criação\n\n**Aluno:** João Vitor Lacerda — RM 565565 — 2TDSPW",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "tutorId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "clinicaId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "petId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "consultaId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "vacinaId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "medicamentoId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "agendamentoId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "alertaId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (admin)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', function(){ pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var data = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('token', data.token);",
                  "pm.test('token salvo', function(){ pm.expect(data.token).to.be.a('string'); });"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (user)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"user\",\n  \"password\": \"user123\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register novo usuário",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"novo_user\",\n  \"password\": \"senha123\"\n}" }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Tutores",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar tutores (paginado + filtros)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tutores?page=0&size=20&sort=nome,asc&nome=&email=",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","tutores"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "0" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "sort", "value": "nome,asc" },
                { "key": "nome", "value": "" },
                { "key": "email", "value": "" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Buscar tutor por ID",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tutores/{{tutorId}}" }
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar tutor",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tutores",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nome\": \"Carlos Mendes\",\n  \"cpf\": \"529.982.247-25\",\n  \"email\": \"carlos@email.com\",\n  \"telefone\": \"11988887777\",\n  \"endereco\": \"Rua dos Lirios, 50\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) { var d = pm.response.json(); pm.collectionVariables.set('tutorId', d.id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Atualizar tutor",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/tutores/{{tutorId}}",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nome\": \"Carlos Mendes Junior\",\n  \"cpf\": \"529.982.247-25\",\n  \"email\": \"carlos@email.com\",\n  \"telefone\": \"11988887777\",\n  \"endereco\": \"Rua dos Lirios, 50\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
